Qrest must be compiled using a Qt 4.2 or higher compile chain.

I) Compile Qrest application
===============================

    a) get to folder containing 'qrest.pro' file
    b) type `qmake qrest.pro` (beware of using a 4.2 or higher qmake)
    c) type `make`
    
    created executable : qrest

II) Compile Qrest unit tests
===============================

    a) get to folder containing 'tests.pro' file
    b) type `qmake tests.pro` (beware of using a 4.2 or higher qmake)
    c) type `make`

    created executable (Will launch all unit tests and print report on standard output) : qrest_unit_tests

thanx for any comment or constructive criticism sent to fcornu@wardsback.org

